These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
House: colonial, tower, farmhouse, greening
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, december, july, february
4 different games are played: poker, go, billiard, domino
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, green, purple, chestnut
1. the person who's birthday is in december is the colonial house##1
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who likes green##1
3. the person playing billiard is the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the greening house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the right of the tower house##1
6. the person playing poker is on the left of the person playing go##1
7. the person who's birthday is in december is the person who likes light-blue##1
8. the person playing go is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
9. the greening house is on the left of the person who likes purple##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| House         | colonial  | greening  | tower | farmhouse |
| Birthday           | december | september | february  | july  |
| Game   | domino       | billiard      | poker | go      |
| Color           | light-blue          | green     | purple    | chestnut     |

