.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, scooter, quad-bike, snowmobile
4 different games are played: chess, bridge, scrabble, go
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower, balloon-flower, aconite
House: art-deco, modern, cape-cod, victorian
1. the person playing chess is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsaconite is the art-deco house##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the right of the person driving the car##1
4. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
6. the person driving the quad-bike is the person who growsballoon-flower##1
7. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
8. the cape-cod house is on the left of the person driving the car##1
9. the art-deco house is on the right of the victorian house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Transport      | quad-bike     | car       | scooter | snowmobile        |
| Game          | go     | bridge       | scrabble   | chess   |
| Flower   | balloon-flower      | bellflower       | aconite     | iris    |
| House         | cape-cod | victorian | art-deco | modern |

