.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, american, chinese, colombian
City: venice, hamburg, rome, paris
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, snowboarding, badminton, weightlifting
There are 4 different favourite colors: blood-red, emerald, apricot, lilac
 1. the colombian is the person who likes lilac##1
 2. the chinese is on the far right##1
 3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
 4. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 5. the french is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 6. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 8. the chinese is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
 9. the french is on the left of the person who likes lilac##1
10. the chinese is the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Nationality      | american | french       | colombian        | chinese        |
| City           | hamburg   | rome | venice   | paris |
| Sport   | biathlon     | snowboarding    | weightlifting | badminton        |
| Color           | apricot         | blood-red  | lilac       | emerald         |

