.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-4::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, banana, cucumber, radish
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, baseball, tennis, golf
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, game, alhambra, ritmeester
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: superhero, crime, adventure, drama
1. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person eating peas##1
2. the person eating cucumber is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the far right##1
4. the person eating radish is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
5. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person eating banana##1
7. the person eating radish is on the right of the person eating peas##1
8. the vegafina-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person watching adventure movies is the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food           | banana   | peas  | radish | cucumber |
| Sport   | tennis | golf       | baseball       | surfing     |
| Cigar   | alhambra       | ritmeester    | game     | vegafina  |
| Movie-Genre           | crime     | adventure | drama     | superhero         |

