.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
City: marseilles, london, colone, new-york
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, sudoku, puzzles, woodworking
There 4 different types of food: raspberry, asparagus, banana, eggplant
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, may, october, november
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
4. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating raspberry##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person who's birthday is in november##1
6. the person who's birthday is in november is the person eating banana##1
7. the person eating raspberry is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
8. the person traveling to london is on the right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
9. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person traveling to colone##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| City           | marseilles  | colone    | london | new-york |
| Hobby   | puzzles      | sudoku    | rock-climbing         | woodworking    |
| Food   | asparagus   | raspberry     | banana          | eggplant      |
| Birthday         | may | march | november      | october      |

