 7. the cain-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
 8. the colombian is on the right of the polish##1
 9. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
