.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, tram, taxi, jet-ski
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, punk, metal, gospel
There are 4 different favourite colors: pink, red, white, blue
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, peas, watermelon, lime
1. the fan of gospel is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the person driving the ship is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the taxi is the fan of gospel##1
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who likes red##1
6. the fan of punk is on the left of the person eating peas##1
7. the person who likes blue is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
8. the fan of punk is the person driving the jet-ski##1
9. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person eating lime##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Transport      | ship     | jet-ski           | tram    | taxi    |
| Music-Genre         | metal  | punk | salsa  | gospel |
| Color   | white     | pink     | red | blue   |
| Food         | lime | broccoli     | peas | watermelon     |

