6. the owner of the bird is on the left of the tiparillo-smoker##1
7. the person playing go is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
8. the tiparillo-smoker is on the far right##1
9. the person who's sport is climbing is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | montecristo | dunhill     | baccarat       | tiparillo |
